p; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; nginx.ingress.kubernete=
s.io/ssl-redirect: true<br>Events: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp=
