<p>ex: kubectl describe ingress -n rtf ext-rtf-ingress-template</p>
<p>Name: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ext-rtf-ingress-template=
<br>Labels: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;none&gt;<br>Namespace: &=
